Brief history
-------------
* Old versions of MPINT: Perl + GNUplot; work fine, but not too user-friendly 
* Version 1.0 = re-written in Python, tested on datafiles from CZ, IT, ES
* Version 1.1 = small improvements of code + improved documentation

